HTTP401.accessTokenExpired:
Access token has expired at unix time.

HTTP500.systemError:
An unexpected error has occurred. 
Please contact the administrator.

HTTP502.badGateway:
Communication with the server failed. 
If this occurs repeatedly, please contact the administrator.

HTTP504.gatewayTimeout:
The server did not accept the request within the hour. 
There may be temporary access congestion. 
Please try executing again after a while.
